### Variables (automatically loaded from .env if present)
@baseUrl = https://api.dnb.nl
@subscriptionKey = {{$dotenv DNB_SUBSCRIPTION_KEY_DEV}}

### 1. Test Echo API (Connectivity Check)
GET {{baseUrl}}/echo-api/helloworld
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}

### 2. Get Statistics Metadata (Schema Discovery)
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/v2024100101/metadata
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 3. Query Statistics Data (Example Dataset)
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/v2024100101/data?dataset=banking-sector&limit=5
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{subscriptionKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 4. Test via Toolbox (Local MCP Server)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/tool/dnb-statistics-metadata/invoke
Content-Type: application/json

